---
import Container from './layout/Container.astro';
---

<section class="bg-slate-900 py-16 text-slate-100 sm:py-20 lg:py-24" aria-labelledby="how-it-works-title">
  <Container size="wide">
    <h2 id="how-it-works-title" class="text-3xl font-semibold">How It Works</h2>
    <p class="mt-2 max-w-2xl text-sm text-slate-300">No generic consulting. Clear scope, implementation, and delivery.</p>
    <ol class="mt-8 grid gap-5 lg:grid-cols-3">
      <li class="rounded-2xl border border-slate-700 bg-slate-800/60 p-6">
        <p class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-wide text-emerald-300">1. Quick Technical Review</p>
        <p class="mt-2 text-slate-200">Short assessment call plus a structured review of your setup, data flow, and accessibility risks.</p>
      </li>
      <li class="rounded-2xl border border-slate-700 bg-slate-800/60 p-6">
        <p class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-wide text-emerald-300">2. Fixed Scope & Delivery Window</p>
        <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-slate-300">If the scope is unclear, we stop and clarify it first.</p>
        <p class="mt-2 text-slate-200">Clear deliverables, fixed pricing, and a defined 3-7 day delivery window.</p>
      </li>
      <li class="rounded-2xl border border-slate-700 bg-slate-800/60 p-6">
        <p class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-wide text-emerald-300">3. Implementation & Handoff</p>
        <p class="mt-2 text-slate-200">Implementation, validation, and delivery notes you can use right away.</p>
      </li>
    </ol>
  </Container>
</section>
